    "description": "At CES 2020, Samsung announced its new lineup of TVs. At the top is a stunning 8K QLED TV with bezels that are nearly invisible. And theres also The Sero, a 43-inch TV that rotates vertically to play content from your phone.  Read more:   Subscribe:  Like The Verge on Facebook:  Follow on Twitter:  Follow on Instagram:   Why'd You Push That Button Podcast:  The Vergecast Podcast:  More about our podcasts:   Read More:  Community guidelines:  Wallpapers from The Verge:   Subscribe to Verge Science on YouTube, a new home base for our explorations into the future of science:",
